1.2 Work with the files

1.

  for (i in 1:length(files)) {
    file_name <- files[i]
    file_type <- substr(file_name, nchar(file_name) - 3, nchar(file_name))
    pathed_name <- paste("../Problem Set 3 Materials/", file_name, sep="")
    
    if (file_type == '.jpg') {
      pic <- image_read(pathed_name)
      cat(file_name, "\n")
      plot(pic)
    } else if (file_type == '.pdf') {
      page2 <- image_read_pdf(pathed_name, pages = 2)
      plot(page2)
      cat(file_name, "\n")
    } else {
      cat(file_name, "cannot be displayed \n")
    }
  }
## DOC 1.docx cannot be displayed 
## DOC 2.docx cannot be displayed 
## DOC 3.docx cannot be displayed

2 Control structures

1.

  sentences <- ifelse (
    substr(files, nchar(files) - 3, nchar(files)) == ".jpg",
    paste(files, "is an image file \n"),
    ifelse (
      substr(files, nchar(files) - 3, nchar(files)) == ".pdf",
      paste(files, "is a pdf file \n"),
      paste(files, "is something else \n")
      )
    )
  cat(sentences, "\n")
## DOC 1.docx is something else 
##  DOC 2.docx is something else 
##  DOC 3.docx is something else 
##  PDF 1.pdf is a pdf file 
##  PDF 2.pdf is a pdf file 
##  PDF 3.pdf is a pdf file 
##  Photo 1.jpg is an image file 
##  Photo 2.jpg is an image file 
##  Photo 3.jpg is an image file 
##

2.

  num_png <- 0

  for (i in 1:length(files)) {
    file_name <- files[i]
    file_type <- substr(file_name, nchar(file_name) - 3, nchar(file_name))
    if (file_type == '.png') {
      num_png <- num_png + 1
    } 
  }

  if (num_png == 0) {
    cat("There are no png files \n")
  } else if (num_png == 1) {
    cat("There is a single png file \n")
  } else {
    cat("There is", num_png, "files \n")
  }
## There are no png files

3.2

1.

files <- list.files("../Problem Set 3 Materials")
num_imgs <- 0
num_pdfs <- 0
num_other <- 0
for (i in 1:length(files)) {
    file_name <- files[i]
    file_type <- substr(file_name, nchar(file_name) - 3, nchar(file_name))
    if (file_type == '.png' || file_type == '.jpg') {
      num_imgs <- num_imgs + 1
    } else if (file_type == '.pdf') {
      num_pdfs <- num_pdfs + 1
    } else {
      num_other <- num_other + 1
    }
}
